' description: sdk-bridge resume / recovery sequence — 3 段 (主路径 / 自愈链 / 收尾)
' last_updated: 2026-05-29
@startuml sdk-bridge-resume-recovery-flow

title sdk-bridge resume / recovery — sequence (3 段, claude / codex 双端镜像)

actor Caller as C
participant "sdk-bridge facade" as SB
participant "内存 sessions Map" as SMap
participant "自愈层\n(recoverer)" as Rec
participant "数据表 (会话)" as DB
participant "会话管理器" as SM
participant "SDK 子进程" as SDK
participant "jsonl 文件" as Fs

== 段 1: 主路径 (内存活) ==

C -> SB: sendMessage(sessionId, text)
SB -> SMap: sessions.has(sessionId)?

alt 主路径 (内存活)
  SMap --> SB: internal { permissionResponder, inputStream, ... }
  SB -> SDK: pushUserMessage(text) → SDK stdin write
  SDK --> SMap: 'assistant' / 'user' / 'result' messages
  SMap --> C: emit AgentEvent
else 断连 → 进自愈
  SMap --> SB: undefined
  SB -> Rec: recoverAndSend(sessionId, text)
end

== 段 2: 自愈链 (单飞 + cwd + jsonl 兜底) ==

Rec -> Rec: recovering.set(sessionId, promise) (单飞锁同步注册)
note right of Rec
  防 archived session 并发 sendMessage 双 createSession
end note

' LO1: recoverer 入口先 emit user message + attachments 再做 cwd precheck (保证 cwd 全 miss / createSession fail 时用户气泡不丢)
Rec -> SMap: emit role='user' message (含 attachments)\n[claude recover-and-send-impl.ts:109-139 / codex 同款 110-135]
note right of Rec
  入口先 emit user message → 保证 cwd 全 miss / createSession fail
  情况下用户气泡仍入库,前端不丢
end note

Rec -> DB: sessionRepo.get(sessionId) → cwd / permissionMode / lifecycle / archived_at
opt row.archived_at != null (archived 自愈)
  Rec -> DB: sessionRepo.unarchive (恢复对话身份连续性)
end

' M5: PLACEHOLDER_DEDUP_MS=5_000 5s 窗口防快速并发触发同 sid 多次 emit
Rec -> SMap: emit 占位 message '⚠ SDK 通道已断开,正在自动恢复…' (非 error 占位)
note right of SMap
  **5s dedup 窗口防快速并发触发同 sid 多次 emit**
  (PLACEHOLDER_DEDUP_MS=5_000, constants.ts:58 + recover-and-send-impl.ts:229-235)
  placeholderEmittedAt Map 记录,5s 内同 sid 再触发 skip emit
end note

' cwd 启发式 fallback
Rec -> Fs: cwdExists(row.cwd)?
opt cwd 失效 (worktree 已被删除 / 跨设备同步丢)
  Rec -> Rec: 启发式找仍存在的祖先目录
  alt 找到 fallback
    Rec -> SMap: emit info '⚠ cwd 失效,自动回退到 <fallback-cwd>'
  else 找不到
    Rec --> C: emit error '⚠ cwd 失效且无法回退' + reject
  end
end

' jsonl-missing fallback
Rec -> Fs: jsonl 文件存在?
alt jsonl 不存在 (CLI --resume 撞 'No conversation found')
  Rec -> SB: maybeJsonlFallback (走 fresh-cli-reuse-app — applicationSid 不变)
  SB -> SDK: createSession(opts) resumeMode='fresh-cli-reuse-app'\n+ resume=applicationSid (传 applicationSid 复用应用层身份)
  SDK --> SB: newRealSessionId (fresh thread,与 OLD_CLI_ID 不同)
  SB -> SM: updateCliSessionId(applicationSid, newRealSessionId)\n(applicationSid 不变 / 不迁子表,仅 cli_session_id 替换)
  SB -> SM: markRecentlyDeleted(OLD_CLI_ID) 60s blacklist (防 ghost session)
  SB -> SMap: sessions key 不变 (applicationSid stable)
  opt claude 端
    Rec -> Rec: prependHistorySummary 拼接 history 摘要 prepend 到首条 prompt
    note right of Rec
      prependHistorySummary 5 失败状态 (CHANGELOG_107 引入):
      - api-error / oversized / parse-error / placeholder-only / empty-history
      失败时降级仅 emit 占位,不阻塞 fresh fallback 主链路
    end note
  end
  note right of Rec
    codex 端精简版无 LLM 摘要 prepend
    (codex-jsonl-fallback.ts:116-141 同款 finalSessionId 不变)
  end note
else jsonl 存在 + cwd valid (正常 resume)
  Rec -> SB: createSession(resume, prompt, cwd, permissionMode)
  SB -> SDK: createSession 带 --resume
  SDK -> Fs: read jsonl 复原历史
  SDK --> SB: realSessionId (first realId — spawn 路径 temp → real)
  opt realId != opts.resume (CLI 软 fork — spawn 首次拿 first real id)
    SB -> SM: releaseSdkClaim(OLD) + renameSdkSession(OLD, realId)\n(spawn temp rename: DB record + 子表整体迁移)
    note right of SM
      claude SDK 在 streaming input + resume + 新 prompt 下行为不可控
      可能给新 session_id (与官方 SDK 文档不符,实测铁证)
      此路径为 spawn 首次 createSession 拿 first real id 时用,
      与 fresh-cli-reuse-app + updateCliSessionId(applicationSid 稳定) 不同
    end note
  end
  SB -> SMap: sessions.set(realId, internal)
end

== 段 3: 收尾 ==

Rec -> SB: 回主路径 sendMessage(text) push 进 SDK
SB -> SDK: stdin write
SDK --> SMap: response messages → emit AgentEvent
Rec -> Rec: recovering.delete finally (单飞锁释放,成功/失败都释)

@enduml
